      "content": "i get that, but it feels like a lot of the \"net positive\" stuff is pretty theoretical and hard to measure, whereas the cost of the actual compliance is happening right now. could u dig a bit deeper into the specific economic downsides for these small shops? like, what are the actual risks to their business models?",
